Advertise
The Emory Wheel offers various advertising opportunities for anyone seeking to connect with the Emory Community through the Wheel’s extensive marketing platforms. Whether in our bi-weekly campus newspapers (printed and distributed around Emory’s Clifton (Atlanta) and Oxford (Covington) Campuses on select Wednesdays throughout the Fall and Spring academic semesters) or on our well-trafficked website, advertising with the Wheel is sure to result in quality marketing exposure from both the Emory University and greater Atlanta consumer markets. And what’s more, we can accommodate almost any advertising budget with our affordable marketing vehicles.
To start advertising with us today, see the information linked below.
Advertising Information & Rates
Please find our current Media Kit
here
. All advertising rates listed in the document are subject to change
Sponsored Content Inquiries
If you are interested in publishing sponsored content (sponsored articles and/or sponsored link placements) on our website, please fill out our
Sponsored Content Interest Form
. All sponsored content inquiries should be submitted exclusively via this form.
Contact
For all other advertising and general business inquiries, please c
ontact our Business Manager, Hunter Collins, at
hunter.collins@emory.edu
; all inquiries will be directed to an appropriate account executive.
Deadlines
All print advertising requests must be submitted via email by 6 p.m. on the Friday before a newspaper publication date.
Print artwork is due by Noon on the Monday before a newspaper publication date.
